article_title: Charitable pharmacy helps to put prescriptions within reach

article_metadata.description: It's not fancy. It offers no tabloid magazines, lipstick, candy or sweatshirts for sale, but that's the point. The services being offered at the Prescription Assistance Network of Stark County matter much more than the ambiance.
article_metadata.author: Charita  Goshay
